blocks.en:
flowchart TD
  A[Frame to send] --> B{Group addressed or Beacon?}
  B -->|Yes| C[Use a basic rate / basic MCS]
  B -->|No, individually addressed| D{Receiver rates known?}
  D -->|Yes| E[Any rate the receiver supports]
  D -->|No| F[Fall back to basic / mandatory rate]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
  A[待发送的帧] --> B{组播帧或信标帧?}
  B -->|是| C[使用基本速率 / 基本 MCS]
  B -->|否, 单播帧| D{已知接收方速率?}
  D -->|是| E[接收方支持的任意速率]
  D -->|否| F[回退到 基本 / 强制 速率]
